#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-ops/src/bk_ops_guide.xml3010(para)
msgid ""
"A plugin for the nova volume manager. Provides support for a new and "
"specialized types of back-end storage."
msgstr ""
"nova ボリュームマネージャのプラグイン。プラグインにより新しい種類や特別な種類"
