"む。"

#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-ops/src/bk_ops_guide.xml355(glossterm)
msgid "auditor"
msgstr "auditor"

#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-ops/src/bk_ops_guide.xml357(para)
msgid ""
"A worker process that verifies the integrity of swift objects, containers, "
"and accounts. Auditors is the collective term for the swift account auditor, "
