#: doc/src/docbkx/openstack-ops/src/ch_ops_network_troubleshooting.xml317(para)
msgid ""
"If your instances are still not able to obtain IP addresses, the next thing "
"to check is if dnsmasq is seeing the DHCP requests from the instance. On the "
"machine that is running the dnsmasq process, which is the compute host if "
